### Hey!
I’m currently redesigning this website. If you’re looking for my blog, you can find some of the posts on [Medium](http://medium.com/@des_cho). If you’d like to see my portfolio, please [request it](mailto:d.chongarova@gmail.com) and I’ll send it to you straight away. Here are a few other places where you can find me:
- [LinkedIn](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/descho)
- [Twitter](https://twitter.com/des_cho)
- [Instagram](http://instagram.com/descho/)
- [GitHub](https://github.com/descho/)
